status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.

comments.comment: Attached a patch which checks if any region is still in transition (in the region server side) before getting the online region list. If there is a region in transition, it means the region hasn't been moved to the online region set yet after the znode is moved to OPEN. If that's the case, that explains why this test is rare to fail.
Jimmy Xiang go for it

Patch is integrated into trunk and 0.95. Thanks Stack for the review.
Will leave the issue open for a while.
